<blockquote><b>Prompt:</b> Design an app for touch devices that uses Inking (Pen based input on digital canvas) as the primary way of input and creation.</blockquote> <br>

<div class="videoWrapper"><center><iframe width="640" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/FkqE6ea_p9M" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></center></div> <br><br>

<p> <b>Motivation:</b> The need and motivation for a mobile/wearable experience prototyping tool supporting motion gesture prototyping came from the following understanding. If motion gestures were to become a common interaction modality, the underlying question was how to equip designers with tools that can support the motion gesture design process.</p> <br>

