<p><b>Perform Action on certain text: Change Mode -> Select -> Gesture</b></p>
<div class="row" style="padding:10px; background-color: #f5f5f5">
  <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-4"> Users can mark certain parts of text so that they can refer to it later. They can select that text and perform actions like highlighting, calculation, etc., in this example user wants to mark a formula so that he can refer to it later. </div>
